Definition: large shrub or shrubby tree having sharp spines and pinnate leaves with small deciduous leaflets and sweet-scented racemose yellow-orange flowers
Example: grown as ornamentals or hedging or emergency food for livestock; tropical America but naturalized in southern United States
Synonyms: horsebean, Parkinsonia_aculeata, shrub, genus_Parkinsonia, m, large, or, shrubby, tree, having, sharp, spines, and, pinnate, leaves, with, small, deciduous, leaflets, sweet-scented, racemose, yellow-orange, flowers, grown, as, ornamentals, hedging, emergency, food, for, livestock, tropical, America, but, naturalized, in, southern, United, States
Category: noun.plant
